  "details": "A vulnerability was detected in Edimax BR-6675nD 1.12. This vulnerability affects the function formsetPPPoE of the file /goform/formsetPPPoE of the component POST Request Handler. Performing a manipulation of the argument pppUserName results in buffer overflow. It is possible to initiate the attack remotely. The exploit is now public and may be used. The vendor was contacted early about this disclosure but did not respond in any way.",
